and france it was the first such meeting here since 1971 
earlier west german chancellor helmut kohl insisted german 
reunification will come one day but acknowledged such a step 
remains a vision 
the meeting was held at allied headquarters in west berlin 100 
miles inside east german territory at the 1971 meeting an 
agreement was drawn up establishing the rights of the four 
countries in the city which has been divided into four sectors 
since world war ii 
