militants had demanded safe passage for their colleagues freed in 
the swap they had agreed to reduce their demand to freedom for 
five militants he said 
earlier in the day a bomb exploded inside an air cargo complex 
in srinagar injuring at least 15 people and severely damaging the 
building officials said no one claimed responsibility and it was 
not immediately known if the blast was related to the kidnapping 
jammukashmnir is the only moslem majority state in the 
officially secular predominantly hindu india moslems make up 64 
percent of the state but nationwide comprise only 11 percent of the 
population hindus comprise 80 percent of indias 880 million 
people 
kashmir is claimed both by india and pakistan and the two 
