foundation a nonprofit educational and scientific organization 
that promotes free enterprise 
the government is sending commodities and expertise to poland 
but there was no provision in the law for the inputs such as 
machinery fertilizer and feed needed to make a modern farm 
system work auspitz said 
polish banks he said dont have the money to loan against next 
years harvest to enable the farmers to buy those input items 
fertilizers animalcare products animal feed pesticides 
fungicides and herbicides top the list of items polish farmers 
need also needed is machinery such as planters grain drills 
potato seeders fertilizer spreaders manure spreaders plows 
