learn about problems facing women there 
cline said she has retired at least six times but cant make it 
stick she stays involved to feel like im worth something have 
something to offer and have a place in this world 
virginia yaeger 65 of des moines raised two children after 
her divorce by working as a dental assistant at age 60 she was 
forced out of her job when her boss retired i tried to find work 
with another dentist but they all wanted to hire younger dental 
assistants yaeger said 
